# Mobile-First Layout

Every view, layout, and component in the guest and guide apps MUST be designed mobile-first. These apps are primarily consumed on mobile devices.

- Start with the mobile layout, then add responsive breakpoints for larger screens.
- Touch targets must be at least 44x44px.
- Avoid hover-only interactions — they don't work on touch devices.
